Responsibilities

  Oversees project controls for the project
  Responsible for planning and scheduling, cost estimating and monitoring of projects
  Establish operating policies to mitigate risk.&nbsp;
  Provide guidance and consultation to project managers on scheduling and costing matters
  Resolving issues arising from operation

Requirements

  Degree in Engineering / Business Management
  Min. 10 years experience in Project Control in the oil and gas industry
  Willing to be based in Jurong Island
  Willing to take on 2-3 &nbsp;years contract&nbsp;
